8866/22/13)</option>\r\n                                        <option value=\"43292\" >ΧΑΤΖΗΠΕΤΡΟΥ ΑΙΚΑΤΕΡΙΝΗ (Ε64437/1/24)</option>\r\n                                        <option value=\"43293\" >ΧΑΤΟΥΠΗ ΑΝΑΣΤΑΣΙΑ ΑΝΤΩΝΙΑ (Ε64438/1/24)</option>\r\n                                        <option value=\"38638\" >ΧΡΙΣΤΟΔΟΥΛΙΔΗΣ ΓΕΩΡΓΙΟΣ (Ε39364/01/19)</option>\r\n                                        <option value=\"42330\" >ΧΡΙΣΤΟΔΟΥΛΟΥ ΜΑΡΙΑ (Ε58746/01/23)</option>\r\n                                        <option value=\"42253\" >ΧΡΙΣΤΟΠΟΥΛΟΣ ΚΩΝΣΤΑΝΤΙΝΟΣ ΚΛΕΩΝ (Ε40527/01/20)</option>\r\n                                        <option value=\"41602\" >ΧΡΙΣΤΟΠΟΥΛΟΣ ΓΕΩΡΓΙΟΣ ΑΝΔΡΕΑΣ (Ε49370/01/23)</option>\r\n                                        <option value=\"42044\" >ΧΡΙΣΤΟΠΟΥΛΟΥ ΙΩΑΝΝΑ (Ε54183/01/22)</option>\r\n                                        <option value=\"43961\" >ΧΡΥΣΑΚΗ ΕΛΕΝΑ (Ε65070/1/25)</option>\r\n                                        <option value=\"43962\" >ΧΡΥΣΑΝΘΟΠΟΥΛΟΥ ΝΙΚΟΛΙΤΣΑ (Ε65071/1/25)</option>\r\n                                        <option value=\"41997\" >ΨΙΜΑΡΝΗΣ ΜΙΧΑΗΛ (Ε54136/01/21)</option>\r\n                                        <option value=\"43294\" >ΨΥΧΟΓΥΙΟΥ ΑΙΚΑΤΕΡΙΝΗ-ΠΑΝΑΓΙΩΤΑ (Ε64439/1/24)</option>\r\n                                    </select>\r\n                <div class=\"mt-1\"><em><small>Ο <strong>υπεύθυνος βάρδιας</strong> έχει αντίστοιχα δικαιώματα με τον <strong>υπεύθυνο αποστολής</strong>, για τη συγκεκριμένη όμως βάρδια.  Αν έχετε ορίσει υπεύθυνο αποστολής, αυτός ορίζεται ως προεπιλεγμένος και στη νέα βάρδια, μπορείτε όμως να ορίσετε ως υπεύθυνο βάρδιας διαφορετικό άτομο.</small></em></div>\r\n                <div class=\"input-field\">\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"col s12 m12 l4 pt-5\">\r\n            <div class=\"col s12 m-0\">\r\n                <label class=\"label-clear\" for=\"shift_start_date\">Έναρξη Βάρδιας</label>\r\n                <input name=\"shift_start_date\" id=\"shift_start_date\" type=\"date\" class=\"validate\">\r\n                \r\n                <!-- <em><small>min length 6 - max length 60. Should start with an english letter and should be followed by english letters, numbers, - or _ </small></em> -->\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"col s12 m12 l4 pt-5\">\r\n            <div class=\"col s12 m-0\">\r\n                <label class=\"label-clear\" for=\"shift_end_date\">Λήξη Βάρδιας</label>\r\n                <input name=\"shift_end_date\" id=\"shift_end_date\" type=\"date\" class=\"validate\">\r\n                \r\n                <!-- <em><small>min length 6 - max length 60. Should start with an english letter and should be followed by english letters, numbers, - or _ </small></em> -->\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"col s12 m12 l4 pt-5\">\r\n            <div class=\"col s12 m-0\">\r\n                <label class=\"label-clear\" for=\"total_participants\">Μέγιστες συμμετοχές</label>\r\n                <input name=\"total_participants\" id=\"total_participants\" type=\"number\" min=\"1\" value=\"1\" class=\"validate\">\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col s12 pt-2 nodisplay\" >\r\n        <div class=\" col s12 m-0\">\r\n        <label class=\"label-clear\" for=\"comments\">Σχόλια Βάρδιας</label>\r\n          <textarea name=\"comments\" id=\"comments\" class=\"materialize-textarea\"></textarea>\r\n          \r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <!-- <div class=\"row  pt-5 nodisplay\" >\r\n          \r\n    </div> -->\r\n    <div class=\"row nodisplay \" >\r\n        <div class=\"col s12 m12 l12 pt-5\">\r\n            <div class=\"col s12 m-0\">\r\n                <span class=\"sidebar_title\"><strong>ΩΡΕΣ ΒΑΡΔΙΑΣ</strong></span>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>  \r\n        <div class=\"col s12 m12 l4 pt-5\">\r\n            <div class=\"col s12 m-0\">\r\n                <label class=\"label-clear\" for=\"hours_volunteering\">Εθελοντικές</label>\r\n                <input name=\"hours_volunteering\" id=\"hours_volunteering\" type=\"number\" min=\"0\" value=\"0\"class=\"validate\">\r\n                \r\n                <!-- <em><small>min length 6 - max length 60. Should start with an english letter and should be followed by english letters, numbers, - or _ </small></em> -->\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"col s12 m12 l4 pt-5\">\r\n            <div class=\"col s12 m-0\">\r\n                <label class=\"label-clear\" for=\"hours_sanitary\">Υγειονομικές</label>\r\n                <input name=\"hours_sanitary\" id=\"hours_sanitary\" type=\"number\" min=\"0\" value=\"0\" class=\"validate\">\r\n                \r\n                <!-- <em><small>min length 6 - max length 60. Should start with an english letter and should be followed by english letters, numbers, - or _ </small></em> -->\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"col s12 m12 l4 pt-5\">\r\n            <div class=\"col s12 m-0\">\r\n                <label class=\"label-clear\" for=\"hours_training\">Εκπαιδευτικές</label>\r\n                <input name=\"hours_training\" id=\"hours_training\" type=\"number\" min=\"0\" value=\"0\" class=\"validate\">\r\n                \r\n                <!-- <em><small>min length 6 - max length 60. Should start with an english letter and should be followed by english letters, numbers, - or _ </small></em> -->\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"col s12 m12 l4 pt-5\">\r\n            <div class=\"col s12 m-0\">\r\n                <label class=\"label-clear\" for=\"hours_retraining\">Επανεκπαίδευσης</label>\r\n                <input name=\"hours_retraining\" id=\"hours_retraining\" type=\"number\" min=\"0\" value=\"0\" class=\"validate\">\r\n                \r\n                <!-- <em><small>min length 6 - max length 60. Should start with an english letter and should be followed by english letters, numbers, - or _ </small></em> -->\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"col s12 m12 l4 pt-5\">\r\n            <div class=\"col s12 m-0\">\r\n                <label class=\"label-clear\" for=\"hours_tep\">ΤΕΠ</label>\r\n                <input name=\"hours_tep\" id=\"hours_tep\" type=\"number\" min=\"0\" value=\"0\" class=\"validate\">\r\n                \r\n                <!-- <em><small>min length 6 - max length 60. Should start with an english letter and should be followed by english letters, numbers, - or _ </small></em> -->\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"col s12 m12 l4 pt-5\">\r\n            <div class=\"col s12 m-0\">\r\n                <label class=\"label-clear\" for=\"hours_lifeguard\">ΝΑΥΑΓΟΣΩΣΤΙΚΕΣ</label>\r\n                <input name=\"hours_lifeguard\" id=\"hours_lifeguard\" type=\"number\" min=\"0\" value=\"0\" class=\"validate\">\r\n                \r\n                <!-- <em><small>min length 6 - max length 60. Should start with an english letter and should be followed by english letters, numbers, - or _ </small></em> -->\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <div class=\"error\" id=\"errormsg\"></div>\r\n    <div class=\"col s12 pt-1 nodisplay\" >        \r\n        <p><input type=\"submit\" name=\"submit\" value=\"ΑΠΟΘΗΚΕΥΣΗ\" class=\"btn\"></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n</form>\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\n    .nodisplay{\r\n        opacity: 0;\r\n    }\r\n</style>\r\n<script>\r\n$(function () {\r\n\r\n    //construct an array of mission_types to use it to determin hour types:\r\n    //var mission_types_str = '[\"Item\", \"Count\"],[\"iPad\",2],[\"Android\",1]';\r\n    var mission_types_str = '[\"71\", \"hours_training\"],[\"56\", \"hours_volunteering\"],[\"57\", \"hours_volunteering\"],[\"36\", \"hours_training\"],[\"86\", \"hours_training\"],[\"33\", \"hours_training\"],[\"83\", \"hours_volunteering\"],[\"60\", \"hours_lifeguard\"],[\"85\", \"hours_tep\"],[\"16\", \"hours_sanitary\"],[\"81\", \"hours_retraining\"],';\r\n    mission_types_str = mission_types_str.slice(0, -1); \r\n    var mission_types_arr = JSON.parse(\"[\" + mission_types_str + \"]\");\r\n\r\n    $(\"select\").formSelect();\r\n    shift_start_date = flatpickr(\r\n        document.getElementById('shift_start_date'),{\r\n            altInput: true, \r\n            altFormat: \"d-m-Y H:i\", \r\n            enableTime: true, \r\n            time_24hr: true,\r\n            minDate: '2026-05-12', \r\n            maxDate: '2026-05-12',\r\n            onClose: function(selectedDates, dateStr, instance) {\r\n                shift_end_date.set('minDate', dateStr);\r\n                shift_end_date.setDate(dateStr);\r\n            },\r\n        }\r\n    );\r\n    \r\n    shift_end_date = flatpickr(\r\n        document.getElementById('shift_end_date'),{\r\n            altInput: true, \r\n            altFormat: \"d-m-Y H:i\", \r\n            enableTime: true, \r\n            time_24hr: true, \r\n            minDate: '2026-05-12', \r\n            maxDate: '2026-05-12'\r\n        }\r\n    );\r\n\r\n    \r\n    // $.validator.addMethod('mission_type_valid', function(value, element) {   \r\n    //     if(value == \"\") return false; else return true;\r\n    // }, 'Επιλέξτε τύπο βάρδιας');\r\n\r\n    \r\n    //$(\"#add_mission_shift\").validate();\r\n    //return;\r\n\r\n    $( \"#mission_type_id\" ).change(function() {\r\n        $('.nodisplay').css('opacity', '1');\r\n        \r\n    });\r\n\r\n    $( \"#shift_start_date\" ).change(function() {\r\n    //console.log($( \"#shift_start_date\" ).val() );\r\n    //shift_end_date.set('minDate', new Date( $( \"#shift_start_date\" ).val() ) );\r\n    });\r\n\r\n    $( \"#shift_end_date\" ).change(function() {\r\n        //populate hours based on hour time and difference between datetime fields:\r\n        selected_mission_type_id  = $( \"#mission_type_id\" ).val();\r\n        console.log(\"selected_mission_type_id: \"+selected_mission_type_id);\r\n        if( selected_mission_type_id != \"\"){\r\n            var selected_hour_type;\r\n            for( var i = 0, len = mission_types_arr.length; i < len; i++ ) {\r\n                if( mission_types_arr[i][0] === selected_mission_type_id ) {\r\n                    selected_hour_type = mission_types_arr[i][1];\r\n                    console.log(mission_types_arr[i]);\r\n                    break;\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n            if(selected_hour_type != \"\"){\r\n                dfrom = new Date( $( \"#shift_start_date\" ).val() );\r\n                dto = new Date( $( \"#shift_end_date\" ).val() );\r\n                hours = Math.ceil( Math.abs(dto - dfrom) / 36e5 ) ;\r\n                $(\"#\" + selected_hour_type).val(hours);\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n\r\n    $( \"#add_mission_shift\" ).submit(function( event ) {\r\n\r\n        \r\n        event.preventDefault();\r\n        $(\"#errormsg\").text(\"\");\r\n        if($('#mission_type_id').find(\":selected\").val() == \"\"){\r\n            $(\"#errormsg\").text(\"Επιλέξτε τύπο βάρδιας\");\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        if($('#shift_start_date').val() == \"\"){\r\n            $(\"#errormsg\").text(\"Συμπληρώστε την Έναρξη Βάρδιας\");\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        if($('#shift_end_date').val() == \"\"){\r\n            $(\"#errormsg\").text(\"Συμπληρώστε τη Λήξη Βάρδιας\");\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n\r\n        showOverlay();\r\n            $.ajax({\r\n               type: 'POST',\r\n               url: base_url+\"ajaxdptadmin/MissionAddShift\",\r\n               data: {\r\n                    'mission_id': $( \"#mission_id\" ).val(),\r\n                    'mission_type_id' : $('#mission_type_id').val(),\r\n                    'admin_member_id' : $('#admin_member_id').val(),                    \r\n                    'shift_start_date' : $('#shift_start_date').val(),\r\n                    'shift_end_date' : $('#shift_end_date').val(),\r\n                    'total_participants' : $('#total_participants').val(),                    \r\n                    'hours_volunteering' : $('#hours_volunteering').val(),\r\n                    'hours_sanitary' : $('#hours_sanitary').val(),\r\n                    'hours_training' : $('#hours_training').val(),\r\n                    'hours_retraining' : $('#hours_retraining').val(),\r\n                    'hours_tep' : $('#hours_tep').val(),\r\n                    'hours_lifeguard' : $('#hours_lifeguard').val(),\r\n                    'comments' : $('#comments').val(),\r\n                    'rccrmtk': '97e207ce4d14c885347fd4e942d05a4c',\r\n               },\r\n               success: function(response, newValue) {\r\n                 hideOverlay();\r\n                 //console.log(response);\r\n                  var result = $.parseJSON(response);\r\n                  if (result.status == -1) {\r\n                   bootbox.alert(result.title);\t\t\t\t\t\t\t  \r\n                  }else{\r\n                    Swal.fire(\"Results\", \"Η προσθήκη της Βάρδιας ολοκληρώθηκε.\", \"success\").then((value) => {\r\n                        location.reload();\r\n                      });\r\n                  }\r\n               },//end of success\r\n                error: function(response, newValue) {\r\n                  hideOverlay();                                    \r\n                    if (!response.success) {\r\n                        Swal.fire(\"Results\", \"Παρουσιάστηκε σφάλμα. Παρακαλούμε δοκιμάστε αργότερα.\", \"error\").then((value) => {\r\n                      });\r\n                    } else {                                        \r\n                        Swal.fire(\"Results\", \"Παρουσιάστηκε σφάλμα. Παρακαλούμε ανανεώστε τη σελίδα και δοκιμάστε ξανά.\", \"error\").then((value) => {\r\n                        location.reload();\r\n                      });\r\n                    }\r\n                },//end of error\r\n            });//end ajax\r\n        \r\n        \r\n    });\r\n});\r\n</script>"
        },
